original_title: Austin Dean Ashford: Live at the Lilypad
overview: Austin Dean Ashford is no stranger to the stage. His special stage is performed live from the Lilypad in Cambridge, Massachusetts.
tagline: Latin Grammy nominated Austin Dean Ashford blows your mind with his comedy, rapping and insane beatboxing ability, all while playing a ukulele.
title: Austin Dean Ashford: Live at the Lilypad
